tracks.text: Light reflects off metallic surfaces
Michael Bublé sings in close up
Flourescent lights illuminate metal duct work across the ceiling of a factory
Documents marked Top Secret pan by, including maps, photos, and a briefcase
Silhouettes of 6 women pose in front of a purple background
The Hydra logo, from the Marvel universe
Michael Bublé stands in a suit in front of a silver Jaguar E-Type Series 3. Behind him, red lights flicker against a factory.
Bublé walks down a cement hallways
He walks through a door marked Level 1. Women in white spandex talk in the factory. He sneaks behind them.
The spandex women walk around, carrying billy clubs. He slides behind duct work.
Men in hard hats sit at a control station.
Bublé approaches a board, looks around, and presses buttons.
An Asian woman looks through a telescope lens. Bublé appears in focus, and turns to look at us.
The men in hard hats get up from the control station and step away. Bublé appears behind them and approaches the terminal
Sirens blare. He looks up
He turns away, jumps over a railing, adjusts his tie, and casually walks away
3 women in white spandex with batons run down the hallway. Steam fills the view.
The hard hat men drive a truck. Bublé rounds a corner, and the 3 women stand, looking at him.
The hard hat men stop and look surprised. Bublé fights the women in a stylized, cardboard cut-out rendering of comic book violence.
Bublé adjusts his tie, and the hard hat men run.
Bublé walks away. The 3 women lie sprawled on the ground. Their spandex suits show the Hydra logo.
Bublé sings to us as he walks casually down the hallway. Sirens blare around him.
Women pose in silouette.
A pressure gauge approaches red
Bublé runs. A digital clock counts down 3, 2, 1. Top Secret documents burn.
Bublé goes to open the Jaguar's handle, then pulls his hand back and shakes it
Bublé's photo is one of the documents burning
He gets in the Jaguar, which becomes fully transparent
